INFORMATION

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

CHANGES

* Version 1.0.0 (2021-12-18)
C: Add support for Debian 11 (Bullseye)
C: Drop support for Debian 10 (Buster)

* Version 0.1.3 (2020-12-20)
E: Remove default conf.d and conf-enabled directories
E: Adapt monitrc configuration file to Debian template

* Version 0.1.2 (2020-12-19)
E: Adapt monitrc configuration file to Debian template

* Version 0.1.1 (2020-12-18)
B: Install Monit from 'buster-backports' APT repository

* Version 0.1.0 (2020-12-15)
F: Initial release
